&Q000473 = A hymn to Enki (?) for Išme-Dagan (Išme-Dagan X)
@composite
#project: epsd2/literary
#atf: use unicode
#atf: use math
#etcsl: text-id=c.2.5.4.24
#key: after http://etcsl.orinst.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/etcsl.cgi?text=c.2.5.4.24&display=Crit&charenc=gcirc#

1. en eš-bar galam diŋir-re-e-ne sig# nim-ma u₁₈-ru-bi#
#lem: en[lord]; ešbar[decision]; galam[skilful]; diŋir[deity]; sig[weak]; nim[high]; urun[exalted]
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. ešgiri₂! šu du₈ nam-bi tar-tar {d}a-nun-na sub₂-su₈-ub X
#lem: ešgiri[staff]; šu[hand]; du[spread]; nam[fate]; tar[cut]; Anunak[1]DN; sub[imperfect plural stem of ŋen⟦to go⟧]; X
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. me niŋ₂-nam-ma dili-ni zag dib en gal# zi-ŋal₂ ba-X
#lem: me[Being]; niŋnam[anything]; dili[single]; zag[side]; dib[pass]; en[lord]; gal[big]; ziŋal[living things]; X
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. [nam]-diŋir-bi-še₃ 1(AŠ)-a-ni pa e₃ NIŊIN-NIŊIN-bi-še₃ X-[me]-en#
#lem: namdiŋir[divinity]; n; pa[branch]; e[leave]; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=4

5. dug₄#-ga-dug₄-ga-ni niŋ₂-zid mu₂-mu₂ me an ki gen₆-ne₂#-me#-en
#lem: dug[speak]; niŋzid[righteousness]; mu[grow]; me[Being]; an[sky]; ki[place]; gin[confirm]
#etcsl: line-id=5

6. ŋiš-hur bar tam-me! si sa₂-e nun gal-bi zu-zu-me-en#
#lem: ŋešhur[plan]; bar[outside]; tam[clean]; si[horn]; sa[equal]; nun[prince]; gal[big]; zu[know]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. en numun i nam dug₃-bi tud#-tud us₂ dab₅-bi pad₃-pad₃
#lem: en[lord]; numun[seed]; e[bring out]; nam[fate]; dug[good]; utud[give birth (to)]; us[path]; dab[seize]; pad[find]
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. ŋarza mah saŋ-gu₂-ŋal₂-la-bi u₂-gin₇ zid-de₃-eš mu₂
#lem: ŋarza[rites]; mah[great]; saŋguŋal[proud]; u[plant(s)]; zid[right]; mu[grow]
#etcsl: line-id=8

9. ŋidru šum₂-šum₂ aga₃ zid hal-ha mu mah-bi sa₄-sa₄
#lem: ŋidru[scepter]; šum[give]; aga[tiara]; zid[right]; hal[divide]; mu[name]; mah[great]; še[call by name]
#etcsl: line-id=9

10. nam-diŋir-bi ud ul su₃-ra₂-še₃# an# ki-da ŋa₂-ŋa₂
#lem: namdiŋir[divinity]; ud[sun]; ul[distant time]; sud[distant]; an[sky]; ki[place]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=10

11. nun da-ri₂ mu₂-mu₂ A X X X ki za X igi i₃-ŋal₂
#lem: nun[prince]; dari[eternal]; mu[grow]; X; X; X; X; ki[place]; zaza[bow down]; X; igi[eye]; ŋal[⟦be⟧ to be (there]
#etcsl: line-id=11

12. en umuš galam dim₂-ma ŋalga sud ŋeštug₂ bad-e du₇
#lem: en[lord]; umuš[consideration]; galam[skilful]; dimma[thought]; ŋalga[(fore)thought]; sud[distant]; ŋeštug[ear]; bad[open]; du[perfect]
#etcsl: line-id=12

13. diŋir zid A RI X SIG₇-SIG₇ niŋ₂-nam-ma-ni ka-ge-e dib₂#
#lem: diŋir[deity]; zid[right]; X; X; X; X; niŋnam[anything]; kag[mouth]; dib[pass]
#etcsl: line-id=13

14. ad gi₄-gi₄ en a-ga-na# šag₄ kuš₂-u₃ šim-gin₇ ta-ta-hab₂
#lem: ad[voice]; gi[turn]; en[lord]; aga[rear]; šag[heart]; kušu[tired]; šim[aromatic substance]; tahab[soak]
#etcsl: line-id=14

15. nun šag₄ su₃-ra₂ inim-ma nu-[kam₃]-me nam-zu-ni daŋal bur₂
#lem: nun[prince]; šag[heart]; sud[distant]; inim[word]; kam[alter]; namzu[wisdom]; daŋal[wide]; bur[spread out]
#etcsl: line-id=15

